# PRD Changelog
**Date:** December 16, 2025
**Version:** 2.0 Updates

## 12-12-25 (PRD Meeting)

### Feature Tiers & Gating
- **Differentiation:** Clear delineation required between Free and Paid tiers.
- **Gating:** Advanced modules and Certifications are strictly paid features.

### Onboarding & User Flows
- **Personas:** Stylist, Salon Owner, Certification Client.
- **Tours:** Pop-up guided tours for new users.
- **Assessment:** Extended skill assessment (beyond original 3 questions).

### Training Modules
- **Structure:** Customizable structures (Collections vs Modules) per salon/client.
- **Tracking:** Detailed progress tracking (checklists, %) and Salon Owner monitoring.
- **Prerequisites:** Toggleable logic per module (flexible learning paths).

### Content Delivery
- **Drip:** Schedule-based release or all-at-once options.
- **Player:** Speed adjustments (0.5x-2x), Force minimum watch time.

### Analytics (Salon Owners)
- **Engagement:** Detailed stylist engagement capability.
- **Completion:** Overall module completion rates.

### Certification Program
- **Phasing:** Initial launch: "The Bob". Future: Pixie, Shag, etc.
- **Commerce:** Distinct pricing and Stripe flows per certification.
- **Physical:** Automation for shipping certificates/rewards.

### Payment & Subscription
- **Platforms:** Stripe (Web/Android), Apple IAP (iOS).
- **Pricing:** Potential markup for iOS to offset 15-30% fees.

### Directory
- **Access:** Public web portal + In-app.
- **Roadmap:** Direct client-stylist connection.

---

## 12-15-25 (Meeting with Ray)

### Lesson Content Enhancements
- **Attachments:** PDF upload/download support.
- **Rich Media:** Lessons now support Video + Text Blocks + Inline Images (not just video).

### Event & Workshop Management
- **Creation:** UI with Start/End times, auto-Stripe price ID generation.
- **Virtual:** Zoom integration (auto-link delivery).
- **Discovery:** Event calendar with preview videos.
- **Discounts:** Automated member discount application.

### Ticketing
- **Management:** In-app PDF tickets, Email delivery.
- **Future:** QR code scanning (Phased).

### Notification & Engagement
- **Cadence:** Configurable triggers (1 week, 24hr, 1hr).
- **Controls:** Quiet hours, Frequency caps, User toggles.

### Access & Content Organization
- **Collections:** New organizational unit for video/content access. Can be assigned directly to bypass paywalls.

### Certified Stylist Directory
- **Features:** Map & Search, Profiles (Bio, Instagram, Badges).
- **Automation:** Post-certification notifications.

### Platform & Policy
- **Fees:** researching waivers for Apple 15%.
- **Architecture:** Split iOS/Android apps with shared root.

### Analytics & AI
- **Dashboard:** Combined Revenue, Location, Churn, Conversion.
- **AI:** Scope added for backend workflows and future chatbot.

